works.description:
This is Mahakaleshwar Murti. This item is
 
specially for aghori, tantrik upasak and mahakal sadhaks.This murti is
made  
by pure mercury mixed with vishnukaant stone. This murti is very effective
 
for Mahakal Rituals, Tantrik Prayogs and Aghor Kriya.  It gives quick  
benefit in tantra prayog and rituals. If you are invoking for doing ritual
 
since long time but not getting success so you should do daily worship by 

tantrik widhi for this Mahakal Murti and in front of this murti you should
 
do your sadhna and rituals. In short time you will get success in ritual  

and also tantra. for best result offer wine and meat daily to Lord Mahakal
 
Murti. Also removes all type of problems in life, gives success in  
materialistic world and salvation to invoker. This murti is highly  
effective and favorite item of Tantrik, Aghoris and Sadhaks. This item  
always you can see near asharam, pilgrimage and near all tantric.
